OL,3,CGunman who charged dinner attended by
OL,4,CDonald Trump was 'lone wolf whack job'
OL,6,FA gunman armed with "multiple weapons"
OL,7,Fwho tried to charge a Washington
OL,8,Fdinner attended by Donald Trump was "a
OL,9,Flone wolf whack job", according to the
OL,10,FUS president.
OL,12,FThe White House Correspondents'
OL,13,FAssociation dinner was thrown into
OL,14,Fchaos by the attack on Saturday night
OL,15,Fand saw the American leader, who has
OL,16,Fbeen the previous target of an
OL,17,Fassassination attempt, swiftly
OL,18,Fevacuated by secret service agents
OL,19,Falong with other senior members of the
OL,20,Fadministration.
OL,26,@nD@UOUnD@fO]pD@eOUqD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
