OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777179877
OL,3,CGunman who charged dinner attended by
OL,4,CDonald Trump was 'lone wolf whack job'
OL,6,FOne officer, who was shot but
OL,7,Fprotected by his bulletproof vest, was
OL,8,Ftaken to hospital.
OL,10,FThe suspect, said to have been
OL,11,Fcarrying a shotgun and handgun, has
OL,12,Fbeen identified as Cole Tomas Allen,
OL,13,F31, of Torrance, California.
OL,15,FHe is understood to have been a guest
OL,16,Fin the Washington Hilton hotel where
OL,17,Fthe event was being held and faces
OL,18,Fcharges including assaulting an
OL,19,Fofficer with a dangerous weapon, but
OL,20,Facting attorney general Todd Blanche
OL,21,Fsaid additional charges will be filed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
