OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777179877
OL,3,CGunman who charged dinner attended by
OL,4,CDonald Trump was 'lone wolf whack job'
OL,6,FThe president posted pictures on his
OL,7,FTruth Social platform of the alleged
OL,8,Fassailant handcuffed on the ground
OL,9,Ffollowing his detention.
OL,11,FMr Trump vowed to reschedule the
OL,12,Fdisrupted event at a late-night press
OL,13,Fconference following the shooting,
OL,14,Fwhich he said had "unified" political
OL,15,Fopponents and the media.
OL,17,FHe was attending the annual dinner for
OL,18,Fthe first time as president.
OL,26,@vD@SOUvD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
