OL,3,CGunman who charged dinner attended by
OL,4,CDonald Trump was 'lone wolf whack job'
OL,6,FMr Trump said: "My impression is he
OL,7,Fwas a lone wolf whack job. These are
OL,8,Fcrazy people."
OL,10,FThe president praised the secret
OL,11,Fservice and said the gunman was not
OL,12,Fclose to breaching the ballroom where
OL,13,Fhe sat on stage at the time of the
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,16,FHe added: "I saw a room that was just
OL,17,Ftotally unified. It was, in one way,
OL,18,Fvery beautiful, a very beautiful thing.
OL,26,@nD@POUpD@NO]xD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
