OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777179877
OL,3,CGunman who charged dinner attended by
OL,4,CDonald Trump was 'lone wolf whack job'
OL,6,F"To see a man charge a security
OL,7,Fcheckpoint armed with multiple
OL,8,Fweapons, and he was taken down by some
OL,9,Fvery brave members of secret service,
OL,10,Fand they acted very quickly."
OL,12,FHe added: "It is always shocking when
OL,13,Fsomething like this happens."
OL,15,FWashington mayor Muriel Bowser said
OL,16,Fshe had "no reason" to believe anyone
OL,17,Felse was involved.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@]O]tD@KOUuD@]O]xD@IOUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
