OL,3,CGunman who charged dinner attended by
OL,4,CDonald Trump was 'lone wolf whack job'
OL,6,FMr Blanche said: "Tonight you saw the
OL,7,Fvery worst and the very best of this
OL,8,Fcountry. You saw the very worst by the
OL,9,Factions of that coward... but you also
OL,10,Fsaw the very best because you saw law
OL,11,Fenforcement do exactly what they're
OL,12,Fsupposed to do.
OL,14,F"I promise you justice will be served."
OL,16,FAmong the guests at the black tie
OL,17,Fevent, which Mr Trump said would be
OL,18,Frescheduled in the next 30 days, was
OL,19,Fthe British ambassador Sir Christian
OL,20,FTurner.
OL,26,@nD@ROUvD@AOUvD@gO]
