OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777179877
OL,3,CGunman who charged dinner attended by
OL,4,CDonald Trump was 'lone wolf whack job'
OL,6,FThe top diplomat posted on social
OL,7,Fmedia: "The @UKinUSA team attending
OL,8,Ftonight's White House Correspondents
OL,9,Fdinner are grateful for the swift and
OL,10,Fprofessional response of the Secret
OL,11,FService.
OL,13,F"We are thankful that the President
OL,14,Fand all those in attendance were
OL,15,Funharmed & our best wishes are with
OL,16,Fthe injured officer."
OL,18,FThe armed assault comes just days
OL,19,Fbefore the state visit by the King and
OL,20,FQueen, where they are due to meet Mr
OL,21,FTrump and attend a White house banquet.
OL,26,@oD@HOUuD@AOUxD@UO]
