OL,3,CGunman who charged dinner attended by
OL,4,CDonald Trump was 'lone wolf whack job'
OL,6,FThe Washington Hilton has been the
OL,7,Flocation of a previous attempted
OL,8,Fpresidential assassination when then
OL,9,Fpresident Ronald Reagan was shot by
OL,10,FJohn Hinckley Jr outside the hotel in
OL,11,F1981.
OL,13,FIt led to security being ramped up at
OL,14,Fthe property.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
